{"tid":1215041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惠譽：倘香港高度自治受損 或檢視評級","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:56:38.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e35860ad85b5381cf15cb06048b726a9236d55cc","tid":1215041,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"惠譽確認香港長期信貸評級「AA+」，前景為「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽提及《逃犯條例》修訂爭議。該評級機構指出，條例引起市場廣泛討論，憂慮會損害一國兩制下賦予香港的高度自治權。香港目前評級高於中國內地的「A+」，該評級機構解釋，這基於香港的管治水平、法治基礎、政策框架、營商環境及監管制度與中國內地截然不同，即使大灣區令中港經濟融合，亦不會收窄差異。<br />\n<br />\n不過，若內地及香港的體制與監管框架變得相似，會損害香港高度自治，由於香港信貸評級高於中國內地，惠譽或因此檢視香港的評級。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190613/59710457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59710457&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ae438e1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59710457&h=148ed137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190613/59710457</a>"}]}